ntent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD9lOa6g8scXPF_c1mSw_Q4FyPEEXfiX7TadrCB6Fvsjg&oe=67656EF8"}, "display_name": "Aqua Adventure Aquarium", "keywords": ["Aquarium", "Nimo", "Fish", "Sea", "Adventure"], "long_description": "\n**Dive into the Enchanting World of Fish and Sea Creatures at Aqua Adventure Aquarium!** \n\nAre you an Adventure Seeker, Sea Enthusiast, or Casual Observer? Aqua Adventure Aquarium has something for everyone!\n\n**Discover and Explore:**\n-\t**Over 50 Sea Creatures:** Walk around and marvel at 3D models of dolphins, sharks, octopuses, clownfish, whales, and more. Learn fascinating facts about these incredible animals.\n-\t**Shipwreck Reef:** Visit this mysterious area where you might encounter gentle manta rays or come face-to-face with deadly sharks.\n-\t**Abyss Adventure Explorer:** Hold your breath and dive underwater in our Scuba Cart to explore uncharted territories.\n\n**What Aqua Adventure Aquarium Offers:**\n1.\t**3D Aquarium:** Five tanks filled with a variety of fish and sea creatures.\n2.\t**Shipwreck Reef:** Explore a shark-infested shipwreck.\n3.\t**Abyss Adventure Explorer:** Step aboard the Scuba Cart for an up-close encounter with reef and deep-sea creatures. Buckle up for a wild ride!\n", "short_description": "Dive into the Enchanting World of Sea Creatures at Aqua Adventure Aquarium!\n\nDiscover and Explore:\n\u2022\tOver 50 Sea Creatures: Walk around and marvel at 3D models of dolphins, sharks, octopuses, clownfish, whales, and more. \n\u2022\tShipwreck Reef: Visit this mysterious area where you might encounter gentle manta rays or come face-to-face with deadly sharks.\n\u2022\tAbyss Adventure Explorer: Hold your breath and dive underwater in our Scuba Cart to explore uncharted territories.\t"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sanskritisoftwareneha.azurewebsites.net/AquaAdventureAquariumPrivacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://sanskritisoftwareneha.azurewebsites.net/SanskritiS